## Quick Reference Card

### When You See This Error... Try This First:

| Error | First Check | Quick Fix |
|-------|-------------|-----------|
| "No generator found" | Service files | Check META-INF/services |
| "Already executed" | Changelog history | Add runAlways="true" |
| "Objects not found" | Database query | Manual verification |
| "Column not found" | Case sensitivity | Try uppercase |
| "JSON mismatch" | Format structure | Remove metadata |

### Debug Commands Cheatsheet:

```bash
# Check service registration
jar -tf target/*.jar | grep META-INF

# Check execution
mvn test -X | grep -i [YourClass]

# Check database
echo "SHOW [OBJECTS];" | database-cli

# Clean rebuild
mvn clean install -DskipTests

# Full workflow
./scripts/dev-workflow.sh [database] [test]
```

